=== Pronunciation ===

When the notes are sung in different opera traditions, they do not sound as the words would be pronounced in the respective [[varieties of Chinese|regional dialects]]. Instead, they are pronounced in an approximation of [[Modern Standard Chinese]] pronunciation.{{citation needed|date=December 2012}}

